@startuml boundary_route_context_to_dcm_security_session_policy_signal_flow
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true

title Boundary Route Context To DCM Security Session Policy Signal Flow\n(route/alert + boundary/fail-safe context -> DCM security session and policy)

participant "Navigation context" as Nav #F4F7FB
participant "Alert / boundary context" as Boundary #E8F0FE
participant "DCM\ndiagnostic owner" as DCM #E8F7E8
participant "DCM runtime state" as DcmState #FFF4CC
participant "Observers /\ndiag readers" as Obs #FCE8FF

== DCM Inputs ==

Nav -> DCM : frmNavModuleStateMsg\nNavSessionState / NavRouteClass
Boundary -> DCM : frmClusterNotifMsg\nClusterNotifArg
Boundary -> DCM : CoreState::domainBoundaryStatus /\nwarningPathStatus and Core::failSafeMode
activate DCM
DCM -> DCM : routeActive = recent nav session/route class
DCM -> DCM : alertLevel = recent cluster-notif arg
DCM -> DCM : serviceContext =\nethHasBoundaryServiceContext(routeActive, alertLevel)
DCM -> DCM : diagStage = ethDiagBoundaryStage(...)\nfrom route/alert/boundary/fail-safe context
DCM -> DCM : securitySession = 1 when serviceContext,\n2 when diagStage == 1 and routeActive
DCM -> DCM : authState = 1 when serviceContext,\n2 when diagStage == 1
DCM -> DCM : securityFault = ethDiagStageToSecurityFault(diagStage)
DCM -> DCM : securityPolicy = ethDiagStageToPolicy(diagStage)
note right of DCM
Representative gating inputs
- NavSessionState / NavRouteClass
- ClusterNotifArg
- domainBoundaryStatus
- warningPathStatus
- failSafeMode
end note

== Runtime Visibility ==

DCM -> DcmState : securitySession / authState /\nsecurityFault / securityPolicy
note right of DCM
Representative outputs
- securitySession
- authState
- securityFault
- securityPolicy
end note

== Downstream Visibility ==

DcmState -> Obs : diagnostic security visibility /\nservice observers
deactivate DCM

note over Nav, Obs
Representative runtime chain
1. Route, alert, and boundary context reach DCM
2. DCM derives service context and diagnostic stage
3. DCM maps the stage into security session and policy
4. Diagnostic readers observe the effective security posture
end note

@enduml
